\
     - `~/Q/GATHERING/` вАГі workspace root (you are here)\
     - `~/Q/GATHERING/ADLAI` вГ¶Г≤ `~/Q/ADLAI` вГ¶Г≤ `~/Documents/ADLAI` (symlink chain)\
     - `~/Q/GATHERING/CNDCTR` вГ¶Г≤ `~/Q/conductor`\
